range(start, stop, step)

👉 start → where counting begins
👉 stop → where counting stops (NOT included)
👉 step → how numbers change

👉 The stop value is NEVER printed.
'''
n = 5

for i in range(1,n+1):
    for j in range(i,0,-1):# stop just before it j go as per counting
        print(j, end=" ")
    print()


